‚ćĚ Certain operations do not care about real class-based operations, so take care of them here.
‚ćĚ This includes UDP assignments or references, handling non-existent objects, or operating on certain global synthetic actions.
‚ćĚ If nothing needs to be performed here, return ‚éēNULL. Otherwise return the correct ‚ąÜWI result.

 :If obj‚Č°‚éēNULL ‚ćĚ Check for non-existant object processing (a pointer to the parent can't be non-existant)
     :If action‚äā‚ćõ‚ąä'Delete' 'self' ‚ćĚ Special actions where object existence is optional
         :If action‚Č°'self' ‚čĄ result‚Üź'' ‚čĄ :Else ‚čĄ result‚Üź0 0‚ćī'' ‚čĄ :EndIf
         :Return ‚ćĚ Processed; exit with this result
     :Else ‚ćĚ Anything else performed on an undefined object is an error
         Error'‚ąÜWI OBJECT ERROR: Current object undefined'
     :EndIf
 :EndIf

 :If '?'=‚äÉaction ‚ćĚ Asking for system help, but we don't support that
     result‚Üź(1‚Üďaction),' : Help not available'
